  <h2>Symbolism &amp; Meaning</h2>
  <p>
    Black diamonds symbolize strength, devotion, and individuality. Where white diamonds signal brilliance and purity, black diamonds speak to resilience and depth — perfect for couples who value a non-traditional love story with a confident aesthetic.
  </p>

  <h2>Pros &amp; Cons of Black Diamond Engagement Rings</h2>
  <h3>Pros</h3>
